data.description:
Experience the epitome of luxury and comfort in this spacious retreat nestled amidst nature's beauty. Highlights include heated floors in the basement and sunroom, ensuring year-round warmth and comfort, while brand-new kitchen appliances and a tankless water heater offer modern efficiency. Stylish new LVP floors in the basement complement the contemporary charm of the home, while ample storage space caters to all organizational needs. 

Keep your vehicles cozy with the heated attached garage, perfect for chilly winters. Embrace the natural surroundings and observe the abundance of wildlife, enjoying privacy with a neighborhood feel. Maintain lush greenery effortlessly with the convenience of irrigation systems, and for those interested, a charming chicken coop adds rustic charm to the property. Indulge in the perfect blend of luxury, convenience, and natural beauty in this exceptional home. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
